trans-unit.source: Exposes a generic <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> of designer glyphs associated with an activity designer.
trans-unit.target: Activity Designer와 관련된 디자이너 문자의 제네릭 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />를 노출합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection> contains all designer glyphs that appear on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> class with which the collection is associated.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection>에는 컬렉션과 관련된 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner> 클래스에 표시되는 모든 디자이너 문자가 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: You can access the contents of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection> through the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.Glyphs%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection> 속성을 통해 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner.Glyphs%2A>의 내용에 액세스할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class that is empty and has the default initial capacity.
trans-unit.target: 비어 있는 상태에서 기본 초기 용량을 가지는 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class that contains elements copied from the specified generic collection of <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph" />, and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" />의 지정된 제네릭 컬렉션에서 복사된 요소가 포함되어 있고 복사된 요소의 수를 수용하는 충분한 용량을 가지는 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> from which to copy collection elements.

Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> class that contains elements copied from the specified <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: 지정한 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" />에서 복사된 요소가 포함되어 있고 복사된 요소의 수를 수용하는 충분한 용량을 가지는 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerGlyphCollection" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.
